<div class="moto-widget-text-content moto-widget-text-editable">
<ul><li class="moto-text_normal">We will review your medical history to ensure you are fit for donation.</li><li class="moto-text_normal">Your date of birth will be checked to confirm you meet the age requirements for donating blood.</li>
<li class="moto-text_normal">We will inquire about the date of your last blood donation to ensure you adhere to donation frequency guidelines.</li>
<li class="moto-text_normal">Your email address will be collected for communication purposes and follow-up.</li>
<li class="moto-text_normal">Any relevant medical reports will be reviewed to confirm you are in suitable health for donation.</li>
</ul>
