         <div data-widget-id="wid_1555242014_szntjdxt3" class="moto-widget moto-widget-text moto-preset-default  moto-spacing-top-auto moto-spacing-right-auto moto-spacing-bottom-auto moto-spacing-left-auto  " data-widget="text" data-preset="default" data-spacing="aaaa" data-visible-on="mobile-v" data-animation="">
            <div class="moto-widget-text-content moto-widget-text-editable">
                <ul>
                    <li class="moto-text_normal">We’ll sign you in and review the basic eligibility criteria for donating blood.</li>
                    <li class="moto-text_normal">You’ll need to provide a valid form of identification for verification purposes. If you do not have a standard ID, medical proof can be accepted as an alternative.</li>
                    <li class="moto-text_normal">You’ll review important information about the blood donation process to ensure you’re well-informed.</li>
                    <li class="moto-text_normal">We’ll ask for your date of birth to confirm you meet the age requirements for donation.</li>
                    <li class="moto-text_normal">We’ll inquire about the date of your last donation to ensure you are following donation frequency guidelines.</li>

                </ul>
            </div>

